ABOUT PMR EARTH MOVERS

Building Dream into Reality

We, PMR EARTH MOVERS, situated at Chennai, TamilNadu are one of the leading names in providing excavators and earthmoving machinery on hire at affordable rental rates.

We constantly endeavour towards customer satisfaction by delivering services of the best value & quality. The company strives to build sustainable relationships with customers by satisfying their evolving needs.
